{"tid":2173881,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「Lunch哥」扣留期間身體不適 被蒙頭押解往明愛醫院","createTime":"2020-08-25T13:35:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T18:35:07.000Z","uid":240362,"like":38,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"0219037c5045f044f6332bcea94a735d1737acd5","tid":2173881,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T13:35:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/freKJg547nrbh19eJKxO5YTyDsU=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2Z7IVADVNNDYNIBMHGZUPJLZO4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FfreKJg547nrbh19eJKxO5YTyDsU%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2Z7IVADVNNDYNIBMHGZUPJLZO4.jpg&h=9aeb9ad9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有指昨日陳母何姵誼上庭作供時的說法惹起法院外聲援陳彥霖人士的不滿。當何姵誼以及陳的外公等一行人步出法院後，被數名市民追罵、粗言相向及舉中指，更有指陳家屬的車輛一度被阻止駛離。據指，警員今日在死因庭續審的西九龍裁判法院外，拘捕17歲「Lunch哥」 David以及一名中年女子。<br />\n<br />\n大約晚上7點半，人稱「Lunch哥」的李國永，稱扣留期間身體不適，警方召救護車由警署送往明愛醫院治理，被蒙頭的他在兩名警員押解下步下救護車，雙手做出五一手勢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200825/U5KVRCIIPRH2RILSY6ARSUQWRQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200825%2FU5KVRCIIPRH2RILSY6ARSUQWRQ%2F&d=byei43Pfdy9TlHy68xWwXYR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=b66ef575\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200825%2FU5KVRCIIPRH2RILSY6ARSUQWRQ%2F&h=8a7a1a16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200825/U5KVRCIIPRH2RILSY6ARSUQWRQ/</a>"},{"pid":"0d94e2e901ee1f2c4566b119858ae8d023977463","tid":2173881,"uid":59522,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T13:40:39.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aba588ad31daacc6ae1f18270d72d9bc0cd86f47","tid":2173881,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"